{"tid":708912,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)毀滅戰士 強戰世界 狙魔人","createTime":"2018-06-19T15:00:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-19T19:11:39.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"93ed5edc3a982c2492dd157289717be494916c2a","tid":708912,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T15:00:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=%2FQqw8uVibkVPT34cGE9UCfiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=5d7e376a\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=%2FQqw8uVibkVPT34cGE9UCfiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=cb417af3\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=%2FQqw8uVibkVPT34cGE9UCfiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=a67a616e\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵 <br />\n<img src=\"http://a.blog.xuite.net/a/e/2/7/15022789/blog_350122/txt/6830960/0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fa.blog.xuite.net%2Fa%2Fe%2F2%2F7%2F15022789%2Fblog_350122%2Ftxt%2F6830960%2F0.jpg&h=ec6a69d4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://www.movie2free.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/WaroftheWorlds.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.movie2free.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F06%2FWaroftheWorlds.jpg&h=0b222c10&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/5/55/Van_Helsing_poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F5%2F55%2FVan_Helsing_poster.jpg&h=b72c2fbe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.故事發生在火星歐都瓦研究中心，這座研究中心出了非常可怕的事故，一切的實驗都被迫暫停，所有的工作人員也失去聯絡，<br />\n訊號中斷前傳回地球的訊息令人聽了不寒而慄。這是第五級強制隔離行動，只有隸屬海軍陸戰隊的頂尖雷霆小隊，才能使用強大的武力解除危機，至少他們是這麼想的...<br />\n<br />\n2.一架巨型的三腳戰機由地面爆出，並瞬間摧毀了附近的一切，現場頓成人間地獄&hellip;&hellip;原來是火星人想攻佔地球，所以製造一場毀滅地球的浩劫！ Ray（湯姆&middot;克魯斯飾）帶著兒女逃走，這時他才發現保護家人是他唯一的生存職責，為了保護家人安全，Ray縱使自知力量微小，也要和強大的外星人軍隊對抗！<br />\n<br />\n3.凡赫辛為教會委託獵殺異種魔物的獵人，於接受教會委託協助一家族對抗吸血殭屍，之後捲入狼人、科學怪人和德古拉間的風波&hellip;結果竟發現此項任務似乎是命運對其身世的安排&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n11 30PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=%2FQqw8uVibkVPT34cGE9UCfiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=b8af7a66\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=%2FQqw8uVibkVPT34cGE9UCfiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=0e9600db\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2626e584fb5967e45c7b474f60b7101c4cde2f8e","tid":708912,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T15:02:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\